description: That is a frame capture still image from a short moovie shooting with my BMPCC and Lumix 25mm f1.7. I was amazed, how good BMPCC censor reacts for strong and cold direct lights, and makes the skin tones living. Helga, the main actress in the moovie acted like a pro. I‚Äôm glad to work with them! This picture was finalized with Google Nik Pro, heavy detail correction, vignette and changing RGB curves.
